cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CR 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision and deep learning techniques for pedestrian detection, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of synthetic data and domain adaptation techniques, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The application of these techniques to smart cities involves the use of robotics and automation (cs.RO) and cybersecurity (cs.CR), which are also mentioned in the abstract.
